abstract: Islam Karimov wins reelection as president of Uzbekistan by landslide; Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe says results were expected and criticizes election because Karimov, who has history of ruthlessly quashing opposition, left voters without 'genuine political alternatives.'
lead_paragraph: President Islam Karimov has won another term in a landslide, as expected, according to preliminary results issued Monday.
